                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-822-18420131 t18420131-822-punishment-205"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</hi>
